= Installation =

<pre>
$ dnf install python3-pip
</pre>

= Listing installed Packages =

<pre>
$ pip list
</pre>

= Installing a Package =

To install a package:

<pre>
$ pip install <package>
</pre>

To install from a requirements file:

<pre>
$ pip install -r <requirements>
</pre>

